menu "Mic ESP32 Configuration"

config MIC_SETUP_BUTTON_GPIO
    int "GPIO for forced setup button"
    range 0 48
    default 9
    help
        GPIO used for the forced setup long-press input.
        This must be a non-strapping input on your board.
        Do not use GPIO0 on ESP32-S3 boards because it is commonly
        tied to the BOOT button and affects ROM download mode.

endmenu
